<br>
Ancient Spells are compared to Ancient Spells.<br>
<br>
Ancient: Shock of Sun is 258% (ccDPS) of Ancient: Destruction of Ice.  Why?  Destruction of Ice has a hold time.<br>
<br>
Obviously, a wizard would elect not to chain cast it for that reason -- but would instead, alternate spells. <p><table border="0"><tr>
